methods.getNext:
Get the next node after this node.

:return: (IntrusiveDoublyLinkedNode.NODE_TYPE) This node's next node
methods.getPrev:
Get the previous node before this node.

:return: (IntrusiveDoublyLinkedNode.NODE_TYPE) This node's previous node
methods.setNext:
Set this node's next node.

:param other: (IntrusiveDoublyLinkedNode.NODE_TYPE) - This node's new next node
methods.setPrev:
Set this node's previous node.

:param other: (IntrusiveDoublyLinkedNode.NODE_TYPE) - This node's new previous node

text: Interface for allowing sub-interfaces to enforce a common interface for intrusive doubly-linked nodes.
